{"word":"σύρω","slug":"σύρω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σύρω</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to draw, drag</i>, or <i>trail along</i>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to trail along</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to drag by force, hale</i>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b>:—of rivers, <i>to sweep</i> or <i>carry down</i> with them, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be swept away</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}